# Commit allowlist
#
# Keep commits focused on:
# - README.md
# - backend project: dianping-nginx-1.18.0
# - AI subproject: yydp-ai-service
#
# Everything else at the repository root is ignored unless explicitly allowed.
*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/dianping-nginx-1.18.0/
!/dianping-nginx-1.18.0/**
!/yydp-ai-service/
!/yydp-ai-service/**

# Do not commit the frontend / bundled nginx project.
/dianping-nginx-1.18.0/nginx-1.18.0 dianping/

# OS / IDE
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
.vscode/

# Local temp outputs
*.out
*.log
.env
*.env

# Maven / build artifacts
**/.m2-temp/
**/target/
**/build/

# Nginx runtime files
**/logs/
**/nginx.pid

# Local test artifacts
ai_test_report_v2.md
ai_test_results_v2.json
